channel.title: Hamachi ---> No Hamachi
channel.description: Okay so my Co-Owner and I have put together this server and would like to put it online, at first I tried the regular way; but I'm using my neighbors WiFi network and know nothing about it. So I decided to attempt it with Hamachi, and it works great; but nobody uses Hamachi anymore so I was wondering what I can do to make it online the normal/regular way. I'm not on his WiFi at the moment so I can't get the information for ipconfig/all in command prompt. But if you think you can help me my skype is i_am_lil_bizzy or you can pm me. P.s. I know there's the portforwarding method but again I know pretty much nothing about this WiFi
